# React and TypeScript

See [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md).

- Business logic in `src/domain/*` — not in page components
- One source of truth per calculation; prefer pure functions
- Use Supabase generated types; avoid `any` and unsafe casts
- Smallest safe fix; do not rewrite large files
- Match existing import and naming conventions in surrounding code

**Priority pages for stabilization:** inventory count, invoice review, invoices list, dashboard — fix trust before new UI surfaces.
